            , pawnbroker, York-street, Westminster: On the 5th of March, I took in of Mary Jones seven yards and a half of cotton; I lent her fifteen shillings upon it; the little girl, 
               <persName id="t18030420-57-person533">
                  Sarah 
                  Hannegan
               <interp inst="t18030420-57-person533" type="surname" value="Hannegan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030420-57-person533" type="given" value="Sarah"></interp>
